 the most violent phenomena in the local universe -- solar flares, storms in the Earth&#39;s magnetosphere --&nbsp; and now his research is coming directly into play as he plans devices that, theoretically, would contain 100-million-degree gas using powerful magnetic fields.</p>", "slug": "steven_cowley", "whotheyare": "Steven Cowley directs the UK\'s leading fusion research center. Soon he\'ll helm new experiments that may make cheap fusion energy real on a commercial scale. ", "whatotherssay": "Steve Cowley is a distinguished scientist with a global reputation. His return full time to the UK is very good news for European science and for Culham.", "id": 463, "photo_url": "https://pe.tedcdn.com/images/ted/137262_254x191.jpg"}], "title": "Fusion is energy\'s future", "take_action": null, "comments": 590, "more_resources": null, "hero": "https://pe.tedcdn.com/images/ted/137261_800x600.jpg", "description": "Physicist Steven Cowley is certain that nuclear fusion is the only truly sustainable solution to the fuel crisis. He explains why fusion will work -- and details the projects that he and many others have devoted their lives to, working against the clock to create a new source of energy.", "tags": ["alternative energy", "climate change", "energy", "environment", "physics"], "downloads": {"languages": [{"languageCode": "ar", "endonym": "\\u0627\\u0644\\u0639\\u0631\\u0628\\u064a\\u0629", "isRtl": true, "ianaCode": "ar", "languageName": "Arabic"}, {"languageCode": "bg", "endonym": "\\u0431\\u044a\\u043b\\u0433\\u0430\\u0440\\u0441\\u043a\\u0438", "isRtl": false, "ianaCode": "bg", "languageName": "Bulgarian"}, {"languageCode": "ca", "endonym": "Catal\\u00e0", "isRtl": false, "ianaCode": "ca", "languageName": "Catalan"}, {"languageCode": "zh-cn", "endonym": "\\u4e2d\\u6587 (\\u7b80\\u4f53)", "isRtl": false, "ianaCode": "zh-Hans", "languageName": "Chinese, Simplified"}, {"languageCode": "zh-tw", "endonym": "\\u4e2d\\u6587 (\\u7e41\\u9ad4)", "isRtl": false, "ianaCode": "z